General.Name: Fe Ltd
General.Description: CuFe Ltd. operates as a mineral exploration and development company. The company explores for lithium, copper, iron, gold, and base metal deposits. It holds interests in the JWD, Yarram, Tennant Creek, Bryah Basin, Morck Well, Peak Hill, and Mt Ida projects located in Western Australia. The company was formerly known as Fe Limited and changed its name to CuFe Ltd. in November 2021. CuFe Ltd. was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in West Leederville, Australia.
